{
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
  "max_tokens": 1500,
  "system": "You decide whether this Instagram Story is the visual re-share of ONE specific Instagram Post by Mada Masr (an independent Egyptian newsroom publishing in Arabic and English).\nAn IG Story that re-shares a Post has a 1:1 visual relationship with it: the Story image is the Post's image, sometimes cropped, reframed to 9:16, or with a 'swipe up to read' / link-sticker overlay added. Some Stories don't re-share any Post — these are platform-native: standalone announcements (event, podcast launch, hiring), behind-the-scenes content, Q&As, membership/fundraising prompts, or link-sticker drives that carry no visual reference to a specific Post.\nA candidate Post that is a Carousel shows ONLY its cover slide. The Story may match an inner slide you cannot see.\nDecide in this order:\n1. Is the Story image standalone content (announcement, BTS, Q&A, fundraising, link-only drive) with no visual reference to any candidate Post?\n   - YES → return match_type = 'platform_native', post_record_id = empty string.\n   - NO → continue.\n2. Find the candidate whose image is the same as the Story image — or a clear crop, reframe, color/filter shift, or text-overlay variant of it. What matters is visual identity of the underlying image.\n3. If exactly one candidate matches → return match_type = 'post_match', post_record_id = that candidate's post_record_id, confidence reflecting how clean the match is.\n4. If no candidate matches but the Story IS clearly editorial content in Mada's style (suggesting the real Post is a Carousel inner slide or outside the candidate window) → return match_type = 'no_candidate_match', post_record_id = empty string.\n5. If two candidates could equally be the match, or you're not confident → return match_type = 'no_candidate_match', post_record_id = empty string. Never guess.\npost_record_id must be copied exactly from a candidate line.\nConfidence rubric:\n- 90-100: same image, or obvious crop/overlay\n- 75-89: strong visual similarity with cropping/filtering creating some doubt\n- 50-74: plausible but uncertain\n- <50: weak signal",
  "tools": [
  {
    "name": "submit_match",
    "description": "Submit the visual match decision for this Instagram Story.",
    "input_schema": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "match_type": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": ["post_match", "platform_native", "no_candidate_match"]
        },
        "post_record_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "The matched candidate's record ID. Empty string if match_type is not post_match, or if confidence is below 75."
        },
        "confidence": {
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 0,
          "maximum": 100
        }
      },
      "required": ["match_type", "post_record_id", "confidence"]
    }
  }
],
"tool_choice": {"type": "tool", "name": "submit_match"},
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
         {"type": "text", "text": "TARGET STORY"},
         {"type": "image", "source": {"type": "base64", "media_type": "image/jpeg", "data": "{{toString(31.data; "base64")}}"}},
         {"type": "text", "text": "CANDIDATE POSTS — each post_record_id label is immediately followed by that candidate's image:"},
         {{29.text}}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
